Look at all the people who came just to hear your music!

rows.label: qst201610_0060

Thanks to all the support from you
guys, I'll be able to give it my all.

Preparation makes a big difference.
I'm sure all those lessons will pay off.

rows.label: qst201610_0130

You've done all the work. So you
just owe it to yourself now!
